  "comment": "The Showtec Polar 340 WashFX is a powerful and fully featured Flower Wash Moving Head with 8 separately controllable RGBW LED modules, suitable for in- and outdoor applications. Its Individual Pixel Control and LED Ring enable you to create unique and astonishing effects. The Polar 340 WashFX has a wide 4.5° - 35° motorised zoom range, enabling you to seamlessly change every individual module from a narrow beam to a wide wash. Each function and effect, including 8-facet prism with speed adjustable bi-directional rotation, dimmer and strobe, can be controlled via DMX512, Art-Net, RDM, sACN and W-DMX (wireless).",
